Package: file-tool
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.8)
Description: CLI tool for file operations
 A command-line utility that provides tools for common file operations:
  * Create files (empty or with content)
  * Copy files
  * Combine files into one
  * Delete files
 .
 Features include error handling and complete test coverage.